  <div class="content">
    <p>Thank you for your order. Here is everything you need to know about shipping and delivery for Forever Yours.</p>
    <div class="divider"></div>
    <h2>Digital Orders</h2>
    <p>Digital PDF orders are delivered instantly to your email address immediately after purchase. Please check your spam folder if you do not receive your download link within a few minutes. For any issues with your digital order please contact us at <a href="mailto:support@jesusforeveryours.com">support@jesusforeveryours.com</a>.</p>
    <h2>Hardcover Orders</h2>
    <p>Hardcover books are printed on demand and fulfilled through IngramSpark. Please allow 4 to 6 weeks from the date of your order for delivery. You will receive a confirmation email with tracking information once your order has shipped.</p>
    <h2>Shipping Destinations</h2>
    <p>We ship hardcover orders worldwide. Shipping times may vary depending on your location. International orders may be subject to customs fees or import duties which are the responsibility of the recipient.</p>
    <h2>Order Issues</h2>
    <p>If your order arrives damaged or you have not received it within 6 weeks please contact us at <a href="mailto:support@jesusforeveryours.com">support@jesusforeveryours.com</a> and we will do our best to make it right.</p>
    <h2>Returns</h2>
    <p>Because our hardcover books are printed on demand we are unable to accept returns unless the item arrives damaged or defective. Digital purchases are non-refundable once delivered.</p>
    <h2>Contact</h2>
    <p>Questions about your order? Email us at <a href="mailto:support@jesusforeveryours.com">support@jesusforeveryours.com</a> and we will get back to you within 2 to 3 business days.</p>
  </div>